Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan's 'revenue' increases
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043ww1g
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Aug 1982
How the new flexible president won his 'revenue' increases which will help balance the books. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less